</td>
<td style="border-bottom:1px solid black; width:79px; padding:0in 7px 0in 7px; height:43px; background-color:#d0cece; border-top:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-left:none" valign="top">
<p><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="line-height:normal"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:Palatino"><span style="color:black">Gradual, but faster than Alzheimer’s disease</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>
